item.title: elevation-query Readme
item.description: This project originated as the part of my spatialfriend package that retrieved elevation coordinates from various sources locally and around the web. Lately, I’ve been interested in keeping my work in more self-contained modules with lighter dependencies, so I split it out. Table of Contents Introduction Dependencies and Installation Base Installation Extra: Elevation values from Google Maps API Extra: Elevation values from .img and .geotiff files Possible future data sources Example Contact License Introduction “How high up do you think we are right now?
